701942f-b.title: Bronx: University Avenue - Tremont Avenue (West)
701942f-b.text:
1841 University Avenue, west side, north of N. Tremont Avenue,
showing the gate lodge to the large Hugh N. Camp estate snd
driveway. It was destroyed or torn down in 1924. A six-story
apartment, bearing the above street address, 'as later
erected on the site when this area was built up.
E. P. Chrystie  May 30, 1923
